{"tid":590902,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"《新股表現》金貓銀貓(01815.HK)半日收2.41元 高上市價1.3%","createTime":"2018-03-13T05:05:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-13T05:27:17.000Z","uid":70274,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5b0cbf9cc68d79b476fb70d2849af9f1303d66e2","tid":590902,"uid":70274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T05:05:39.000Z","msg":"AASTOCKS<br />\n<br />\n金貓銀貓集團(<a href=\"http://01815.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F01815.HK&d=0DGMe6uSn%2Bd73X8J1m5Ok0bWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=9aff39e8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">01815.HK</a>)暗盤收2.47元，高上市價3.8%；該股首掛開報2.44元，高低見2.5元/2.38元，半日收2.41元，較上市價2.38元，高1.3%；半日成交5,588萬股，涉資1.37億元。<br />\n金貓銀貓為內地線上珠寶零售商。是次來港上市共發售1.94億股，其中10%公開發售獲4.6倍超購，認購一手中籤率70%，股份以接近招股範圍(2.28-3.28元)下限定價，料集資淨額4.1億元，其中65%用作擴展和優化線上線下一體化零售架構，10%用於升級信息技術基礎設施及數據管理系統等。上市獨家保薦人招商證券國際。(sz/a)~<br />\n阿思達克財經新聞<br />\n網址: <a href=\"http://www.aastocks.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.aastocks.com&d=0DGMe6uSn%2Bd73X8J1m5Ok0bWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=eff73411\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.aastocks.com</a>"},{"pid":"49fc2a8a5c1bb2620336346046969f8613bd104e","tid":590902,"uid":90166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T05:08:49.000Z","msg":"個名咁柒都有得升<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc7e024322d7835d9bf42ebc7c4fd504ca3e580f","tid":590902,"uid":132137,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T05:10:24.000Z","msg":"老貓FD?"},{"pid":"1236c89d95b20222afa3a7fa24eaad30c8f0ce7b","tid":590902,"uid":135661,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T05:23:23.000Z","msg":"金貓銀貓賺到錢就係好貓"},{"pid":"619b5b1ec46827a0f0ac4e28d75d91185800e7d4","tid":590902,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T05:27:17.000Z","msg":"垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}